referenceFunction.name: production of carton board boxes, offset printing, at plant
referenceFunction.localName: Produktion von Kartonverpackungen, Offsetdruck, ab Werk
referenceFunction.includedProcesses: This module includes the production of boxes out of cartonboard. It contains the steps of cutting, folding and printing with an offset machine and therefore inks and glues are considered as well as the electricity consumption.
referenceFunction.generalComment: The input of cartonboard is not included into this module allowing the user to establish its own cartonboard boxes. Per kg of used cartonboard, 0.83 kg of this module are needed.

technology.text: Average of the used technology within the examined Swiss producers
